name: Are you looking for a bite or a beating?
description:
I was quietly watching this gentleman through the OVF of my X100S for around five minutes, waiting to get a decent shot of him taking a bite of his sandwich. I had probably taken around 15 photos without him 
noticing me propped up against the wall, he was really into that sandwich. 

From this photo you would imagine that the man on the left, the one looking straight down the lens at me was about to come and ask me what I was doing, but to my surprise he didn't, he just walked straight past me...
